- release 7,
- merged some old BeroLinux de, fr, tr translations,
- added official vim 5.7 patches,
- added sysconfig patch (default [g]vimrc file in /etc/vim and default vim
  menu file is now /etc/vim/menu),
- now vim can be built without athena, motif or gtk subpackages,
- merged docpath and speed_t RH patches (slightly modified),
- some simplifications and cosmetics.
